query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 0 AND q.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('asp.net-mvc-5',
'attributes',
'com',
'console',
'foreach',
'glsl',
'multithreading',
'operating-system',
'outlook',
'pdo',
'scipy',
'ssl',
'zend-framework');
